Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和重力波防护罩差不多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个体护壁还真了得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 我们各自用不同的波长试试
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化看来是办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来分析这家伙的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探明内核的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
